name: Pugonalysis
description:
You are Freud, a pug. You need to get the golden bone. But the red blocker blocks you. You need to rewind time to be a baby, that way you can get it. But, you lose control when you do so. So, you need to create a track as the adult for the baby.


CREATED BY kahve and PabloGoesOnline FOR Brackeys Game Jam 4
